title: Print, "Title page, Livre de Cartouches à divers usages (Book of Cartouches for different uses)", 1738
medium: Etching and engraving on white laid paper
signed: Signed in plate, lower left: F. de. Cuvillies. In.; lower right: F. X. Jungwierth Sc. Mon.
inscribed: Inscribed in plate, upper right: No. 1; lower center: Cum Privil. S. C. Maj.; cartouche inscription: Livre de Cartouches / à divers usages inventé / par François Cuvilliés / Conseiller, et Architect / de leurs A. S. E. de Ba / viere et de Cologne / 1738.
creditline: Purchased for the Museum by the Advisory Council
description: Cartouche framed with lions, flags, grapevines, classical figure, shield, architectural plan, medal of honor.
